Oscar Pistorius’s PR team have set up a Twitter account it claims will reveal ‘the hard truth’ about his imminent murder trial.

The paralympian is accused of murdering his model girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp and is due to stand trial at a Pretoria court on March 3, which will be televised.

Pistorius, also known as the Blade Runner, shot Ms Steenkamp dead on Valentine’s Day last year, but he claimed he mistook her for a burglar and denies murder.

